*irqbalance-0.55-r1 (25 Aug 2007)

  25 Aug 2007; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> +files/irqbalance.1,
  +irqbalance-0.55-r1.ebuild:
  Grab manpage from upstream #169680 by Bryan Veal.

  06 Apr 2007; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  irqbalance-0.55.ebuild:
  ppc stable, bug #160983

  06 Feb 2007; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> irqbalance-0.55.ebuild:
  stable on amd64; bug 160983

  21 Jan 2007; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> +files/irqbalance.confd,
  files/irqbalance.init, irqbalance-0.55.ebuild:
  Drop initd checks as irqbalance itself does it #162975 by J.Taimr.

  09 Jan 2007; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> files/irqbalance.init:
  Abort loading on uniproc/dualcore machines. Only want to run on real SMP
  machines.

  09 Jan 2007; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> irqbalance-0.55.ebuild:
  Stable on x86, bug #160983.

